# Docs Sync — JONBEATZ.DEV

## Version tracking

- Sync version across `package.json`, `TRUTH.md`, `.cursor/docs/MASTER-COMMANDS.md`, README badge.
- Use `npm run version:sync` (Python, UTF-8 safe) — never rewrite README badges from raw PowerShell.
- Run `npm run encoding:check` before doc commits; `npm run docs:sync` runs it automatically.
- `ReCall.md` captures significant session outcomes; `Restore-Points.md` at milestones.

## Backup ritual

- Default destination `G:\Hermes_Project_BackUpz\JonBeatz.dev` (override via `JBD_BACKUP_ROOT`).
- Quick path: `npm run backup:quick` → `jonbeatz-dev-project-v{N}-{a-z}`.
- The backup script refuses to write into the personal `...\JonBeatz` tree (allows `...\JonBeatz.dev`).

## Commit discipline

- Do **not** auto-commit unless Jon asks. Doc-only changes use a `docs:` prefix.
- Update docs when behavior changes (scripts, rituals, deploy).
- No contradictory rules across `.mdc` files.
